    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This vehicle features the S65 4.0L V8, utilizing individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, mated to a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission. This unit is in pristine mechanical and cosmetic order; preventative maintenance is comprehensive, featuring documented rod bearing replacement with high-lead copper shells and upgraded ARP hardware. The factory Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and M-Variable Differential Lock remain perfectly calibrated, ensuring optimal lateral grip and chassis composure. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior demonstrates zero delamination or leather fatigue. A rare, collector-grade specimen for the purist.",
